commit.message: fix to_h to not raise on value being an Array

Rewrite

Simplify Hashr:

* use BasicObject
* remove unused features like :_access and :_include
* remove raise_missing_keys
* rename :define to :default

Merge pull request #10 from jwaterfaucett/fix_deep_symbolize_keys

Fix deep symbolize keys

Raise an ArgumentError when given bad input

when initializing Hashr with data, raise an ArgumentError when the input is garbage
so that its obvious why things don't work.
Previously, there was an undefined method deep_symbolize_keys that was rather cryptic.
